<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .hot-box {
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 300px;
            border: 1px solid black;
            padding: 10px;

        }

        .item {
            display: flex;
            border: 1px solid black;
            align-items: center;

        }

        .title {
            flex: 6;
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        .time {
            flex: 2;
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        .ellipsis {
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="hot-box">
        <div class="item">
            <div class="title ellipsis">가나다라마바사가나다라마바사가나다라마바사가나다라마바사</div>
            <div class="time">2020.05.05</div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <div class="title ellipsis">가나다라마바사가나다라마바사가나다라마바사가나다라마바사</div>
            <div class="time">2020.05.05</div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <div class="title ellipsis">가나다라마바사가나다라마바사가나다라마바사가나다라마바사</div>
            <div class="time">2020.05.05</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>